整体来说，都具有决定性的可能性。</p><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> *本网站上的“NIJISANJI EN（新）”符号是为了与过去存在的原始“NIJISANJI EN（以前的NIJISANJI IN）”区分开来。</p></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://youtube.com/channel/UCV1xUwfM2v2oBtT3JNvic3w" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">辰希 (Selen Tatsuki) [二十三寺 EN]</a> /<a href="https://twitter.com/Selen_Tatsuki" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">辰希 (Selen Tatsuki) <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3c6.png" alt="🏆" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />二十三寺EN</a> / <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/members/selen-tatsuki?filter=NIJISANJI%20EN" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Seren Ryugetsu</a></p> <cite>YouTube / X (Twitter) / NIJISANJI EN（新）</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="uPQpncTKtv"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/anycolor-terminated-nijisanji-en-news-vtuber-selen-tatsuki/">ANYCOLOR 终止 NIJISANJI EN（新）的 VTuber Selen Tatsuki</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 终止了 NIJISANJI EN（新）的 VTuber Selen Tatsuki” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/anycolor-terminated-nijisanji-en-news-vtuber-selen-tatsuki/embed/#?secret=Wqi8YAOyIQ#?secret=uPQpncTKtv" data-secret="uPQpncTKtv" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/">ANYCOLOR 取消了 NIJISANJI EN 所属 VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的合同（新）的帖子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-cont